Put-Directory
    [Tags]    functional
    Comment    Connect and put directory
    Connect To Grid    ${irodshost}    ${irodsport}    ${username}    ${password}    ${zone}
    ${output_base_directory_name} =    Put Directory Into Irods    /iplant/home/${username}    ${put_directory}
